---
import Base from "../../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base title="Visioni della Mente" showFooter={false} dark={true}>
  <article class="project">
    <!-- ── Main grid: cards left / hero right ── -->
    <div class="project-grid">
      <!-- Left: stacked bordered cards -->
      <div class="project-cards">
        <div class="card card--tag">
          <span>(EDITORIAL DESIGN / PUBLISHING PROJECT)</span>
        </div>

        <div class="card card--title">
          <h1 class="project-title">Visioni della Mente</h1>
          <div class="project-subtitle">
            <p>
              la frattura dell'Io: indagine filosofica e artistica nel cinema
              contemporaneo.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card card--body">
          <p>
            This thesis explores cinema as a space where reality fractures and
            the self becomes unstable, fragmented, and uncertain. Through images
            and sounds that blur the line between dream and nightmare, cinema is
            treated as a critical tool to investigate the human mind, memory,
            trauma, and technology. More than entertainment, film becomes a
            philosophical laboratory that questions identity, perception, and
            subjectivity. Combining theoretical research with visual
            experimentation, editorial design, typography, imagery, and short
            films, the project invites the viewer to confront the fragility and
            multiplicity of the contemporary self.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="spacer"></div>

        <div class="card card--tag">
          <span>THESIS EDITION</span>
        </div>

        <div class="card card--body card--upper">
          <p>
            In addition to the editorial work of the written thesis, the project
            also includes a book presenting the practical part.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: hero image -->
      <div class="project-hero">
        <img src="/images/work/01/01-01.webp" alt="Visioni della Mente" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ── Bottom gallery ── -->
    <div class="project-gallery">
      <video src="/images/work/01/01-02.mp4" autoplay loop muted playsinline
      ></video>
      <img
        src="/images/work/01/01-03.gif"
        alt="Visioni della Mente — 3"
        loading="lazy"
      />
      <img
        src="/images/work/01/01-04.webp"
        alt="Visioni della Mente — 4"
        loading="lazy"
        class="img-4"
      />
      <img
        src="/images/work/01/01-05.webp"
        alt="Visioni della Mente — 5"
        loading="lazy"
      />
    </div>

    <!-- Second section -->

    <div class="project-grid">
      <!-- Left: stacked bordered cards -->
      <div class="project-cards">
        <div class="card card--tag">
          <span>Short Film Projects (Practical Thesis Project)</span>
        </div>

        <div class="card card--title">
          <h1 class="project-title">Cruel Creatures</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="card card--body">
          <p>
            No one laughs; the game is never innocent, and freedom is only a
            fragile illusion. Figures move through suspended gardens, sterile
            rooms, pristine forests, and living rooms turned display cases.
            Every gesture carries weight, every action is observed, measured,
            judged. Masks are not ornaments but deforming mirrors, revealing
            hidden power, concealed violence, and the cruelty that hides within
            kindness. These shorts show a world suspended between what we see
            and what escapes, between what exists and what we believe exists — a
            silent, haunting exploration of control, obedience, and the shadows
            of childhood that linger in every gesture.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="spacer"></div>

        <div class="card card--tag">
          <span>Watch the Triller</span>
        </div>

        <div class="card card--body card--upper">
          <p>
            A video project made up of seven short films, each experimenting
            with visual style, mood, and narrative rhythm.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: YouTube embed -->
      <div class="project-hero project-hero--video">
        <iframe
          src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/XWlpv6sNIWY"
          title="Cruel Creatures — trailer"
          allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
          allowfullscreen></iframe>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ── Bottom gallery ── -->
    <div class="project-gallery">
      <video src="/images/work/01/01-06.mp4" autoplay loop muted playsinline
      ></video>
      <video src="/images/work/01/01-07.mp4" autoplay loop muted playsinline
      ></video>
      <video src="/images/work/01/01-08.mp4" autoplay loop muted playsinline
      ></video>
      <video src="/images/work/01/01-09.mp4" autoplay loop muted playsinline
      ></video>
      <video src="/images/work/01/01-10.mp4" autoplay loop muted playsinline
      ></video>
      <video src="/images/work/01/01-11.mp4" autoplay loop muted playsinline
      ></video>
      <img
        src="/images/work/01/01-12.webp"
        alt="Visioni della Mente — 12"
        loading="lazy"
      />
      <img
        src="/images/work/01/01-13.webp"
        alt="Visioni della Mente — 13"
        loading="lazy"
      />
    </div>
  </article>
</Base>

<style>
  /* ── Page shell ── */
  .project {
    background: #000000;
    color: #fff;
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding-top: 96px; /* ticker 26 + nav 56 + 14 breathing */
  }

  /* ── Main grid ── */
  .project-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 20px;
    padding: 24px 24px 10px;
  }

  /* ── Cards column ── */
  .project-cards {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  /* ── Base card ── */
  .card {
    border: 1.5px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 1);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 14px 18px;
  }

  /* Tag pill — self-sizing */
  .card--tag {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    align-self: flex-start;
    padding: 8px 14px;
  }
  .card--tag span {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 1);
  }

  /* Spacer */
  .spacer {
    height: 90%;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .spacer {
      height: 4px;
    }
  }

  /* Title card: two sub-columns */
  .card--title {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0;
    padding: 16px 18px;
  }
  .project-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(20px, 2.2vw, 28px);
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    flex: 0 0 44%;
    padding-right: 20px;
  }
  .project-subtitle {
    flex: 1;
    border-left: 1.5px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);
    padding-left: 20px;
  }
  .project-subtitle p {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
  }

  /* Body text card */
  .card--body p {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  /* Uppercase variant */
  .card--upper p {
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 1);
  }

  /* ── Hero image / video ── */
  .project-hero {
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: 20px;
  }
  .project-hero img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    max-height: 600px;
    object-fit: contain;
    display: block;
  }
  .project-hero--video {
    position: relative;
    aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
    align-self: center;
  }
  .project-hero--video iframe {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    border: none;
    display: block;
  }

  /* ── Gallery ── */
  .project-gallery {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 20px;
    padding: 10px 24px 40px;
  }
  .project-gallery img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    border-radius: 20px;
  }
  .project-gallery video {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    border-radius: 20px;
  }
  .gallery-full {
    grid-column: 1 / -1;
  }

  .img-4 {
    object-fit: contain;
    max-height: 371px;
  }

  /* ── Responsive ── */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .project-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .project-hero {
      aspect-ratio: 4 / 3;
    }
  }
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .project {
      padding-top: 88px;
    }
    .project-grid {
      padding: 16px 16px 8px;
      gap: 8px;
    }
    .project-gallery {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      padding: 8px 16px 32px;
    }
    .gallery-full {
      grid-column: auto;
    }
    .card--title {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 12px;
    }
    .project-subtitle {
      border-left: none;
      border-top: 1.5px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
      padding-left: 0;
      padding-top: 12px;
    }
  }
</style>
